{"tid":2451324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"響應政府首批接種 狂嘔、低燒、關節痛  打科興護士留醫：傷緊個腦","createTime":"2021-03-18T04:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T09:56:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":175,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"cfaad016795ccb255e65d7ac24947f14fd64d8c3","tid":2451324,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/3QK2LHNYFNE6NIAQXF4JD3A2QQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2F3QK2LHNYFNE6NIAQXF4JD3A2QQ%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2f%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=d4dfb8a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2F3QK2LHNYFNE6NIAQXF4JD3A2QQ%2F&h=8931db1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/3QK2LHNYFNE6NIAQXF4JD3A2QQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n響應政府首批接種 狂嘔、低燒、關節痛 <br />\n打科興護士留醫：傷緊個腦<br />\n<br />\n【疫情大反彈】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：第二針將開打 專家：不良反應更勁<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港累計出現七宗接種科興疫苗後死亡個案，嚴重不適者持續增加。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府上月23日就科興疫苗開放予優先群組接受預約接種，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：接種率低 醫護促政府正視數據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2shSrM9YS1Q1_w_961MLsco2xDM=/510x907/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FI5N63JIFNHPNPUYOVJMZYYTY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2shSrM9YS1Q1_w_961MLsco2xDM%3D%2F510x907%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFI5N63JIFNHPNPUYOVJMZYYTY4.jpg&h=162c74d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■該名東區醫院女護士接種科興後疑出現嚴重副作用，目前仍需留醫。 讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n患高血壓 檢測結果陰性<br />\n<br />\n職員續稱，近日事主情況越來越嚴重，不單嘔吐不止，空肚狀態下也嘔吐大作，甚至乏力、腳步不穩、沾寒沾凍、冒汗和關節腫痛。事主曾向同事透露，「覺得傷害緊個腦，不停襲擊個頭，頭好痛，痛到好似撕裂咁」，其上司認為情況嚴重，前日上午安排她入院治理。至當晚事主做血液測試，未發現異常，檢測結果亦為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n據知事主已獲醫生處方止嘔藥和頭痛藥，需吊鹽水補充鉀，稍後或接受腦掃描。她有高血壓，原定下周二（23日）接種第二針，相信要擱置。<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局總行政經理（病人安全及風險管理）何婉霞昨在疫情記者會，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名仁濟護士曾不適送院<br />\n<br />\n何又稱，至今共兩名護士接種疫苗後不適，另一名是仁濟醫院護士，本月8日接。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署公佈，截至昨晚8時的過去24小時，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨向醫管局、衞生署及公務。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E7gZ5PFlM6Q6_e7y7J1J-P4Vf0k=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R6NIJPXMMFD4BF6K7DDRWQBOW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE7gZ5PFlM6Q6_e7y7J1J-P4Vf0k%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR6NIJPXMMFD4BF6K7DDRWQBOW4.jpg&h=f02ed00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事護士（左）為上月首批到中央圖書館接種科興疫苗的醫護人員。"},{"pid":"150faf447d3ec814a2d22679687e03059e6dd583","tid":2451324,"uid":290404,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:32:37.000Z","msg":"呢d野香港d電子傳媒係絕口不提，否則點配合唱紅科興既政治工作呢？"},{"pid":"8d2af033d1a379a8e3963bf5b856616123601e1f","tid":2451324,"uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"吳明德 BionTech與「巴基之星」之雷同走勢，實屬巧合？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2451318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2451318</a>"},{"pid":"23f35bf40f2961bb44925b5142e105ae9073590e","tid":2451324,"uid":230104,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭幾時打第二針？"},{"pid":"4355958d01459a0b37450db0d99d4597984e32af","tid":2451324,"uid":156444,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"是但啦, 打得都代表無腦"},{"pid":"6669f182b70928f94f2da77f1c1d1903837d330a","tid":2451324,"uid":155095,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"選擇打科興嘅本身就冇腦，何來傷腦呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bef519f1b876e1a1a1ec0ea048d69d317a9a784","tid":2451324,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":